                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>

<div class="section-container cutin-top-alt cutout-bottom">
    <section class="section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="has-text-centered section-title">Business challenges</h2>
            <div class="columns">
                <div class="column card">
                    <picture>
      <source type="image/webp" data-srcset="/assets/polygons - 1.webp">
                    <img class="card-image clip-a lazy" src="/assets/polygons - 1.png">
                    </picture>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <h3 class="accent-text">Evidence of date and time</h3>
                        <div class="card-description">
                            <p class="muted">In case there ever is a dispute about the exact time a document was signed, you need to be able to verify this reliably.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="column card">
                    <picture>
      <source type="image/webp" data-srcset="/assets/polygons - 1.webp">
                    <img class="card-image clip-b lazy" src="/assets/polygons - 1.png">
                    </picture>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <h3 class="accent-text">Document authenticity</h3>
                        <div class="card-description">
                            <p class="muted">In case there ever is a dispute about which version of a contract was agreed and signed, you need to be able to validate which one is the original one.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="column card">
                    <picture>
      <source type="image/webp" data-srcset="/assets/polygons - 1.webp">
                    <img class="card-image clip-a lazy" src="/assets/polygons - 1.png">
                    </picture>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <h3 class="accent-text">Document verification</h3>
                        <div class="card-description">
                            <p class="muted">Documents that are shared and used by multiple parties need to be trusted by everyone involved, and independently verifiable.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>

<div class="section-container">
    <section class="section secondary">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="has-text-centered section-title">Solution overview</h2>
            <div class="columns is-centered is-vcentered has-margin-top-40 inverted-mobile">
                <div class="column is-half">
                    <h3 class="title subsection-title dark-indigo">Immutable PDF's</h3>
                    <p class="muted">The document can be represented as a digital fingerprint by 'hashing' the document. LTO Network stores the hash of this document through a with LTO Network connected systems Anyone with access to the data can verify the document by hashing it and comparing it against the stored version.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="column is-1"></div>
                <div class="icon-container solutions column is-centered" style="left:48px; align-self:center;">
                    <div class="livicon-evo" style="position:relative; top:-5px; left:-4px;" data-options="
          name: save;
          size: 130px;
          tryToSharpen: true;
        style: filled;
        fillColor: #ffffff"></div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="columns is-centered is-vcentered has-margin-top-40">
                <div class="icon-container solutions column is-centered" style="left:48px; align-self:center;">
                    <div class="livicon-evo" style="position:relative; top:-3px; left:-5px;" data-options="
              name: clock;
              size: 130px;
              tryToSharpen: true;
              style: filled;
              fillColor: #ffffff"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="column is-1"></div>
                <div class="column is-half">
                    <h3 class="title subsection-title dark-indigo">Verifiable timestamp </h3>
                    <p class="muted">Not only the hashed document (fingerprint) is stored on the blockchain but also the timestamp of the document. By making documents verifiable and independently auditable, they become more valuable. LTO Network creates portable proof of your timestamped claims. These blockchain-based verifications can be shared and transferred to other parties.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="columns is-centered is-vcentered has-margin-top-40 inverted-mobile">
                <div class="column is-half">
                    <h3 class="title subsection-title dark-indigo">No need for third party verification</h3>
                    <p class="muted">Using the on open standards-based LTO Network is, any party can independently verify the authenticity and timestamp of the document, without having to rely on a trusted third party.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="column is-1"></div>
                <div class="icon-container solutions column is-centered" style="left:48px;align-self:center;">
                    <div class="livicon-evo" style="position:relative; top:-3px; left:-12px;" data-options="
              name: notebook;
              size: 130px;
              tryToSharpen: true;
              style: filled;
              fillColor: #ffffff"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="btn-container has-text-centered has-margin-top-40">
                <a href="/contact/" class="button is-primary">Book a demo</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>



